verses.text:
Asaph the chief, and second to him Zechariah, then Jeiel, Shemiramoth,
Jehiel, Mattithiah, Eliab, Benaiah, Obed-Edom, and Jeiel, with stringed instruments and with harps; and
Asaph with cymbals, sounding aloud;

to offer burnt offerings to the LORD on the altar of burnt offering
continually morning and evening, even according to all that is written in the LORD’s law, which he commanded
to Israel;
